    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A totally normal game about 'Rock Paper Scissors'</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game plays like a <u><i>very</i> <i>normal</i></u> Rock Paper Scissors game. <br> <br><strong>Pick your choice </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is nothing else to say here. Just pick between Rock Paper and Scissors aha.<strong> <br> <br>But FIRST, Spam some Gesture with your friend</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>  </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896180/extras/4781a229ce344620957187f01fe769e3.poster.avif?t=1745574232\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896180/extras/4781a229ce344620957187f01fe769e3.webm?t=1745574232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896180/extras/4781a229ce344620957187f01fe769e3.mp4?t=1745574232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>  <br>   </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><br>Hey, it seems that you're winning! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You picked Rock, and your friend picked Scissors, that's great!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But wait... you didn't win yet...<br><br><strong>So it's now time, to smash your friend </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win the quick time event to confirm the victory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remember that you have ALSO to be faster than your friend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896180/extras/eb567fd2e7aa992fa4dac1d13d7c0971.poster.avif?t=1745574232\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896180/extras/eb567fd2e7aa992fa4dac1d13d7c0971.webm?t=1745574232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896180/extras/eb567fd2e7aa992fa4dac1d13d7c0971.mp4?t=1745574232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><br>And if you win...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can finally smash your friend!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896180/extras/65bc96c84a5f50e878b2d09ae04b4bcf.poster.avif?t=1745574232\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896180/extras/65bc96c84a5f50e878b2d09ae04b4bcf.webm?t=1745574232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896180/extras/65bc96c84a5f50e878b2d09ae04b4bcf.mp4?t=1745574232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yeah, that's the general idea ahah.</p>",
